Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:01:01.14,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(30,3000)}{\pos(543,170)}灵风工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:01:01.14,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(30,3000)}{\pos(519,410)}{\fs24}www.fosky.com/bbs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在 再次见到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定又会撒娇的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而无法前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的多摩川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲夏的花依然开放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在707室等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还做了同样款式的浴衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再这样闲逛 我可要先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 有蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又黑又大 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书上有写的 是很有名的蝴蝶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是黑凤蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑凤蝶？不是蝴蝶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫做黑凤蝶的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑凤蝶蝴蝶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟普通的蝴蝶有什么不一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近和五月讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会让我想起以前的真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那家伙只有六岁儿童的程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们又说我什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么系？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要系和小八一样的蝴蝶结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是蝴蝶结 而是叫做花文库的腰带结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是年轻女孩子系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小八也不可以系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（厚脸皮哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是一年一度的多摩川烟花大会的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论大家多么忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这一天 一定会回到这间房子里来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着同样的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以了 就这点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天就开始喝酒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到放烟花就醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 每次见到泰都是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像是活化石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隔了几个月时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会变啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 泰从高中开始就完全没变过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使活到一千岁 一定还是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸也没什么改变呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说身高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很罗嗦唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸 要不要冲个澡 换上浴衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是冲澡 我要沐浴 帮我放水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 遵命 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲呢 今天不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放烟花之前会到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还是那么我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 五月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还穿着浴衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 伸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢这个古装人偶系列了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是给你买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 五月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快谢谢叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时光的流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净化了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈合了内心的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也有无法愈合的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间房子还是跟那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间在这里停住了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实伸他……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸夫怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子浴 很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用这么担心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾也已经准备好了 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是如今 我也有很多话想说给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在这间房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到的却尽是回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然屋里就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要乔装打扮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 八公呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是巧不准她来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他不是那种会为了看烟花这种小事罗嗦的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有联系就是没事的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不祥的证明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这次爽约
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就成了真正的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 无法停止流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为见面说清楚 就能够释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今才明白 在章司身边的那段时光才是最开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司在成为我的恋人以前就已经是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要抛弃内心的芥蒂 仿佛就可以回到从前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而真的是永远失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就该好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（真）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在见到伸 也无法冷静地谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为寂寞 又会向他哭诉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有前科的人要自重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不想又一句话不说地背叛大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去的话 就应该说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jackson的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 快来吧 烟花已经开始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕见到伸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸夫他没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 那家伙也很倔强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说不愿意走入绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（的确如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（的确如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你不用在意他 赶快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真和泰也很期待见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么扫兴 现在才说不来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想快点见到你啊 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里 伸夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都已经说不想见到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还留在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是说怕见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八果然还是很爱你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你一厢情愿的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 我了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕见了面又会迷失的那种恐惧 我最了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和巧的婚礼是在两个星期以后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在又和你旧情复燃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就真的陷入泥沼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她当然会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 那就更不应该见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意和她一起陷入吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你一直以来只是同情被前男友抛弃 又被巧玩弄的小八而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那根本不能算喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是喜欢她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你现在喜欢的是隔壁的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她和我有一样的病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃药就无法工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此她还是很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从前就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢帮助陷入困境的女孩 就算她和自己完全无关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是想充英雄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而一旦发觉自己有可能被牵连进去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸 她只是在挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是轻松的爱情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜真是残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意这样做 想让他们陷入泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出那种话伸当然会认真起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八会比现在更痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸是和平主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他希望大家每天过着幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以努力想选择一条可以得到最好结果的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不认为避免争斗是一件轻松的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和自己的欲望抗争呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 要几份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算逞强 我也要让你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想快点见到你啊 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在跟你旧情复燃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八就会陷入泥沼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有看放烟花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次吃路边摊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是筷子很难用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有提供叉子的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要宠坏他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他练习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然拉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假发会掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小八）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到了门口 但是没人开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非大家都先去看烟花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是房间里还亮着灯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家等不及就先出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才应该道歉 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在哪里看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到你们我再打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？女装？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不原意和她一起陷入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是轻松的爱情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？真？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 大家都在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 真又学美里说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的钻石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼不请伸就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我都不请呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰和真都请了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会唱朋克版的瓢虫桑巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？是什么样的歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会买CD给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你重新编曲 用吉他演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸为了让你得到幸福 才选择退出的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不幸福 他的牺牲就白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过巧的话 一定会让你哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你这么笨 爱上这种人 真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会因为他的一两次婚外恋就受不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以揍他揍到气消为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 河边挤满了人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有看到章司和他的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为一切都落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仿佛稍一侧目就会被冲散的人潮之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想拉住娜娜的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那与伸有着相同体温的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若真的天真烂漫地拉住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让她觉得我反应迟钝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过指间的风 感觉格外地冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天早已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要努力工作咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜比任何人都期望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法挽回的那个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
